  "detailed_description": "<h1>GAME OF MY FRIENDS</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355140/extras/9c43bdefcdcf2bd4e52f7789962c1b49.avif?t=1694986939\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>You're a fleeing delinquent, you're being chased by the police. At the wheel of many cars you try to avoid being caught by the police while collecting as much money as possible!</strong><br><br>Your enrichment will allow you to unlock many more powerful and tougher cars, as well as new maps where your driving skills will be put to the test.<br><br>Choose your getaway vehicle according to its power, life points, handling or the damage it inflicts!<br><br>You will find 2 items on your way. Tools to fix your car and bundles of money to make you rich.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355140/extras/99d9f746311784f80d4d5467d56578dc.poster.avif?t=1694986939\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355140/extras/99d9f746311784f80d4d5467d56578dc.webm?t=1694986939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355140/extras/99d9f746311784f80d4d5467d56578dc.mp4?t=1694986939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Important point: </strong><br>➡ Exclusive map !<br>➡ Steam ranking  !<br>➡ Addictive !<br><br><strong>Will you be the cleverest driver?</strong><br>Share your scores and chase photos in the Steam P.C. community!",
